4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT GENERALLY REVISING LAWS RELATED TO MANUFACTURED
5 AND FACTORY-BUILT HOUSING; REQUIRING THAT MUNICIPAL ZONING REGULATIONS TREAT
