14 Section 1. Section 76-2-202, MCA, is amended to read:
15 "76-2-202. Establishment of zoning districts -- regulations. (1) (a) Within the unincorporated
16 portions of a jurisdictional area that has been established under provisions of 76-1-501 through 76-1-503 or 76-
17 1-504 through 76-1-507 and for the purposes provided in 76-2-201, the board of county commissioners may by
18 resolution establish zoning regulations for a part or all of the jurisdictional area or divide the county into zoning
19 districts with zoning regulations that are considered best suited to carry out the purposes of this part. By
